The Humanities and Social Sciences Library is the largest library at McGill. It supports the teaching, learning, and research activities of staff and students in the Faculty of Arts, the Desautels Faculty of Management, the Faculty of Education, the School of Religious Studies, and the School of Social Work.

The library is a valuable resource for the broader McGill community and visiting scholars and welcomes all members of the public. üíõ
